text.section:
The cabinet shall monitor the establishment of continuing care retirement communities' nursing home beds closely. The cabinet shall collect the following data regarding continuing care retirement communities' nursing home beds:
The number of applications for a certificate of need to convert nursing home beds to nursing facility beds, the number of beds included in each application, and the number of beds approved;
The number of applications for Medicaid certification for continuing care retirement communities' nursing home beds, the number of beds included in each application, and the number of beds certified as Medicaid eligible;
The payor sources for continuing care retirement communities' nursing home beds; and
The number of each type of bed or living unit within each continuing care retirement community on July 14, 2000, and the number of each type of bed or living unit within each continuing care retirement community on October 31, 2003.
